e tools provide you with clear answers about your personal financial situation and offer recommendations for next steps.","AAA Fair Credit offers a variety of courses, seminars and workshops to help improve your financial knowledge. These courses are available online or in-person and cover topics such as setting financial goals, creating spending plans and buying cars."]},"id":"51259d10-4fb5-4ad0-b71c-fddc91b9867e","type":"text"},{"data":{"text":"Fees &amp; Availability"},"id":"cee5430b-2ebd-4542-8ed9-4474e17619ec","type":"heading"},{"data":{"path":"/d2A569Z9Ue5vLkBmiQ2m7E.jpg","link":{"href":"","rel":null,"target":""},"caption":"One of the disadvantages of AAA Fair Credit is that it isn&#39;t licensed to offer its services in all 50 states. It is based in Utah and is also licensed in Arkansas, California, Florida, Georgia, Hawaii and Texas. If you live in those states, you can call for credit counseling sessions and sign up for debt management plans. Counselors are available Monday through Friday from 8 A.M to 5 P.M.","fullscreen":true,"importSrc":"http://www.toptenreviews.com/i/rev/scrn/small/3353-aaa-fair-credit-foundation2.jpg","src":"https://dev.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/d2A569Z9Ue5vLkBmiQ2m7E.jpg","credit":"","align":"","id":"d2A569Z9Ue5vLkBmiQ2m7E","mos":"https://dev.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/d2A569Z9Ue5vLkBmiQ2m7E.jpg","alt":""},"id":"dff855a8-b0ca-4305-8a76-bd1b23c1ccd4","type":"image"},{"data":{"paragraphs":["Debt management plans include setup fees and monthly maintenance fees. Credit counseling agencies cap these fees and waivers are available if your income is 150 percent of the poverty line. AAA Fair Credit has a maximum setup fee of $50 and a maximum maintenance fee of $50."]},"id":"7de86734-44b1-4442-9208-5a37a692951d","type":"text"},{"data":{"text":"Support &amp; Accreditations"},"id":"3ae0e3b2-14a4-4f1f-ba64-e26f1c909524","type":"heading"},{"data":{"path":"/riEJED82RZ8paavaF5q9VH.jpg","link":{"href":"","rel":null,"target":""},"caption":"AAA Fair Credit is 